tasks.prompt:
Create internal/domain/types.go with these types:
- EmailAddress{Name, Address string}
- Message{ID, ConversationID, Subject string; From EmailAddress; ToRecipients, CcRecipients []EmailAddress; ReceivedDateTime time.Time; Body struct{ContentType, Content string}; BodyPreview string}
- Thread{ConversationID, Subject string; Messages []Message}
- QuoteRegion{StartOffset, EndOffset int; AttributedToOrdinal *int; OriginalSnippet string}
- AnnotatedMessage{Message; Ordinal int; QuoteRegions []QuoteRegion; CleanBody string}
- LinearizedThread{ConversationID, Subject string; Messages []AnnotatedMessage}
Follow Go conventions: exported types with doc comments, json struct tags for API fields.

Create internal/render/markdown.go:
- RenderMarkdown(thread domain.LinearizedThread) string — produce full Markdown document
- Format: '# Thread: {Subject}' heading, then '---' separator, then for each message:
  ### Message #{Ordinal}
  **From:** {Name} <{Address}>
  **To:** {comma-separated recipients}
  **Cc:** {comma-separated, omit if empty}
  **Date:** {YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM UTC}
  **Subject:** {Subject}
  \n{CleanBody}\n---
- Handle missing Cc (omit line entirely)
